VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT vTaskPrioritySet\(|xTaskCreate\(|xQueueReceive\(
WHEN EXPR MISSING:assert|check|verify|privilege_check|permission
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects privileged task/queue operations that require security review context.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Freertos FreeRTOS Privileged API Review Marker.
